seo: 金蝶云,任意文件上传,ScpSupRegHandler,漏洞检测
seo_en: Kingdee Cloud, arbitrary file upload, ScpSupRegHandler, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测金蝶云星空系统的ScpSupRegHandler接口是否存在任意文件上传漏洞，并尝试注入内存马以验证漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the ScpSupRegHandler interface of Kingdee Cloud has an arbitrary file upload vulnerability, and attempts to inject a memory webshell for verification.
